1 Installation
**************

Nael's LSP-based features (via Eglot or lsp-mode), require Lean version
4 to be installed (https://lean-lang.org/install/manual/).

   If you prefer third-party lsp-mode over Emacs' built-in LSP-client
Eglot, install ‘nael-lsp’.  You might need to install lsp-mode
beforehand.

